## 1. Project Overview

**QuickPDF Assistant** is a WhatsApp-native PDF automation bot built on top of the **Meta WhatsApp Cloud API**. Users interact with it entirely through WhatsApp — sending documents and selecting options from interactive menus — to perform common PDF operations without needing any desktop software or web app.

### Key Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **Merge PDFs** | Combine 2 or more PDF files into a single document |
| **Split PDF** | Extract a page range (e.g., `2-5`, `1,3`) from a PDF |
| **Compress PDF** | Reduce file size via Ghostscript at three quality levels |
| **Convert: Image → PDF** | Embed a JPG/PNG into a PDF document |
| **Convert: PDF → JPG** | Render PDF pages as JPEG images via Ghostscript |
| **Convert: DOCX → PDF** | Convert Word documents to PDF via LibreOffice |
| **Convert: PDF → DOCX** | Convert PDF to an editable Word document via LibreOffice |
| **Protect PDF** | Encrypt a PDF with a user-chosen password |
| **Unlock PDF** | Decrypt a password-protected PDF |

---

## 2. Architecture Overview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    WhatsApp User                        │
└────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
                         │  HTTPS Webhook (POST/GET)
                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   Express Server (index.js)             │
│   Port: 3000 (default)                                  │
└────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
                         │
                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              routes/webhook.js                          │
│  GET  /webhook  →  Webhook Verification                 │
│  POST /webhook  →  Message Handler                      │
└────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
                         │
                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│           controllers/botController.js                  │
│  • Routes messages by type (text / document / interactive)│
│  • Manages multi-step conversation flow via sessions    │
│  • Orchestrates PDF processing tasks                    │
└───────┬────────────────┬───────────────┬────────────────┘
        │                │               │
        ▼                ▼               ▼
┌───────────────┐ ┌────────────┐ ┌──────────────────────┐
│services/      │ │services/   │ │services/             │
│whatsapp.js    │ │session.js  │ │pdfWorker.js          │
│               │ │            │ │                      │
│ • Send text   │ │ • In-memory│ │ • Merge (pdf-lib)    │
│ • Send lists  │ │   session  │ │ • Split (pdf-lib)    │
│ • Send buttons│ │   cache    │ │ • Compress (gs)      │
│ • Get media   │ │ • Daily    │ │ • PDF↔Image (gs)     │
│ • Download    │ │   usage    │ │ • Protect/Unlock (gs)│
│ • Upload      │ │   tracking │ │ • DOCX↔PDF (soffice) │
│ • Send doc    │ └────────────┘ └──────────────────────┘
└───────────────┘
                         ▲
                         │  Periodic Cron
                         │
               ┌─────────────────────┐
               │  services/cleanup.js│
               │  Purges /tmp files  │
               │  every 15 minutes   │
               └─────────────────────┘
```

